    <item>
      <title>最大铜矿商智利恢复疫情前产量水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/top-copper-miner-chile-gets-back-to-pre-pandemic-output-levels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利的铜产量创下今年最大月度纪录，同时也是疫情爆发以来 10 月份产量最高的一个月，该国最大的电线金属供应国已从项目挫折中恢复过来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/top-copper-miner-chile-gets-back-to-pre-pandemic-output-levels</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 13:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币的“中间派”以太坊在竞争对手的推动下陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/crypto-s-middle-child-ethereum-flounders-as-rivals-gain-ground</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于重新调整的用户体验削弱了活动和费用，以太坊面临着关于其方向的紧迫问题，这引发了人们对区块链是否会继续支撑加密商业的不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/crypto-s-middle-child-ethereum-flounders-as-rivals-gain-ground</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国军情六处负责人警告美国和欧洲不要削减对乌克兰的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/mi6-chief-warns-trump-and-europe-against-cutting-support-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国对外情报机构负责人在唐纳德·特朗普赢得大选后首次公开发表讲话时警告说，如果美国和欧洲停止支持乌克兰与俄罗斯的战争，跨大西洋安全将面临崩溃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/mi6-chief-warns-trump-and-europe-against-cutting-support-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 12:57:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
