      <title>天然气贸易商面临价格高企和管道不确定性的焦虑月份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-11-29/gas-traders-face-anxious-month-of-high-prices-uncertainty-over-russia-pipeline</link>
