      <title>印度经济增长遭遇冲击 央行面临降息压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/india-s-economic-growth-weakens-to-almost-two-year-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度经济增速降至近两年来最低，这抑制了全年经济前景，也考验了总理纳伦德拉·莫迪雄心勃勃的增长计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/india-s-economic-growth-weakens-to-almost-two-year-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 10:41:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区通胀加速但不会阻止欧洲央行降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/euro-zone-inflation-accelerates-but-won-t-derail-ecb-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管欧元区通胀率已超过欧洲央行 2% 的目标，但官员们不太可能在下个月及以后继续降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/euro-zone-inflation-accelerates-but-won-t-derail-ecb-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
