      <title>关税风险和法国政局令欧洲股市暂停</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/european-stocks-pause-as-tariff-risks-french-politics-weigh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周五持稳，投资者在贸易关税担忧和法国近期政治动荡（法国政府难以批准预算）的背景下寻找新的催化剂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/european-stocks-pause-as-tariff-risks-french-politics-weigh</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 08:19:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元结束 8 周连涨势头，美国期货上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/asian-stocks-to-slip-as-treasury-trading-resumes-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，美国股指期货与美国国债期货一起上涨，而市场猜测当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将缓和其最极端的贸易政策，导致美元创下三个月来最大单周跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/asian-stocks-to-slip-as-treasury-trading-resumes-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 22:55:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
